{"tid":145001,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"Diy 修補車身刮花","createTime":"2017-03-06T01:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T05:29:25.000Z","uid":20489,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e233682b04a7acc34899a17bd9f67e4032c5904b","tid":145001,"uid":20489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:43:31.000Z","msg":"架車早排泊街無啦啦比人刮花左<br />\n屌佢老味成3條咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，由右頭沙板去到尾沙板都有。原本已經諗住出街比人搞但無意中係YouTube 見到呢條片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jwbmnWYG2Yg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjwbmnWYG2Yg&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=167447f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jwbmnWYG2Yg</a><br />\n<br />\n咁就膽粗粗去ssp 買野番來試<br />\n<br />\n原本架車係咁<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/06/093435_08edadb4ebcb7223fbe798b074d70a79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F093435_08edadb4ebcb7223fbe798b074d70a79.jpg&h=54577d16&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mkd9t93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMkd9t93.jpg&h=44c67394&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3A8skxD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3A8skxD.jpg&h=585cbbcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始補番油先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q7AgMVu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ7AgMVu.jpg&h=c9252678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n油完大概係咁，之後隔左一日再油多次<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47q9656.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47q9656.jpg&h=33ef011a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/874yQCn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F874yQCn.jpg&h=51d3041d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/06/093706_254323633ef5999077e89299f436dd5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F093706_254323633ef5999077e89299f436dd5b.jpg&h=05ce96de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再等多一日就可以好似條片咁用沙紙momomo<br />\n一開始mo 得太勁搞到有個位無左色，要再油過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMo 番平佢就好似佢咁用個幾支拋光野1，2，3號慢慢抺<br />\n結果就好似下邊咁<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k9vhC10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk9vhC10.jpg&h=fedd8ffd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M2e78fn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM2e78fn.jpg&h=e444a6fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/06/094006_25381b8ee9de84b3c91b404d0fa737ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F094006_25381b8ee9de84b3c91b404d0fa737ab.jpg&h=2d7992d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇相好似ok 但其實未係好好，遲下架車要去打蠟先叫佢去幫手打番好佢，其實如果手工好用呢個方法係應該救得番，但我一向手工都好差所以就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家無野做又時間多又唔水想比錢可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0dd5916bd49f0c7157b2f7fef4c79d25a25f79","tid":145001,"uid":13908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:36:24.000Z","msg":"都算係咁喎"},{"pid":"86d99c4a0d24c8366e6f53dc3f350e7d409f2be1","tid":145001,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:02:21.000Z","msg":"Lm thx樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c104d647b2013544e6fc544b40528a79b69fb2b8","tid":145001,"uid":48980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:36:16.000Z","msg":"之前上網買左隻 冇料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都想試吓呢隻"},{"pid":"1ccebec0fc3d90250419fce586c4020b806aa076","tid":145001,"u