d 沙紙好似45<br />\n加加埋埋200蚊有找</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪係ssp鴨寮街街頭個間汽車精品舖買呀？"},{"pid":"6321b2d75346963d316ca9b5a650b43dba7d209e","tid":145001,"uid":48980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:28:54.000Z","msg":"我搵左好多間汽車舖都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1868f584edc38a1aac1fc474f736830713df18d","tid":145001,"uid":34500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:29:19.000Z","msg":"有支筆 一畫就補到"},{"pid":"4ffb35f4bb522655eae54300add80e8fb61a8a29","tid":145001,"uid":20489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:40:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>到最後我發覺其實唔駛油咁多次<br />\n車尾個條油得太多搞到mo 左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而車頭個條油得最少仲易搞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你買左幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n支油45<br />\n個pack 123 號拋光好似68<br />\n仲有pack 係mo 油用野連埋d 沙紙好似45<br />\n加加埋埋200蚊有找</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪係ssp鴨寮街街頭個間汽車精品舖買呀？</blockquote><br />\n我買個間叫金標誌<br />\n但我無格價"},{"pid":"e3a9dd2c632bebd79c828ff7b362d77416cd6a60","tid":145001,"uid":20489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有支筆 一畫就補到</blockquote><br />\n我都見到有支咁gei 野<br />\n但又無咩介紹所以無買<br />\n可能用個支簡單好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d545639dc1b7446e46abcfff6c5ea552577f0b24","tid":145001,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:27:14.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b046f5a8dc53b2a69bfaf76d62aa76e6a6f4ebaf","tid":145001,"uid":8941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:58:12.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"d80eadec308320f5bc5ed6521e1213a78b4d550a","tid":145001,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T22:38:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lm</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d9e3634bb05a195da1d23fe20f2ac901059ba700","tid":145001,"uid":20489,"like":0,"dislike